rows.label: qst001903_msg0001
rows.name: Hmm? What do you want with me?

rows.label: qst001903_msg0002
rows.name: Oh! The job I gave to Sekaka!

rows.label: qst001903_msg0003
rows.name:
I can't believe you
actually did it. Not bad.

rows.label: qst001903_msg0004
rows.name: Well, it seems he gave up...

rows.label: qst001903_msg0005
rows.name:
I made sure to explain
it to him clearly.

rows.label: qst001903_msg0006
rows.name:
That it would require not
just salvaging, but a Blade.

rows.label: qst001903_msg0007
rows.name:
But you know what? He
wouldn't listen at all.

rows.label: qst001903_msg0008
rows.name:
He just declared, "There's no such thing
as impossible in the dictionary of Sekaka,
the Mushroom-Feast Salvager, mo!"

rows.label: qst001903_msg0009
rows.name:
...Well, enough about that overconfident
Nopon who doesn't listen.

rows.label: qst001903_msg0010
rows.name: I have to pay you your reward.
